1521375410.text: "Apoptosis induced by SLC5A8 and pyruvate in MCF7 cells is associated with up-regulation of p53, Bax, tumor necrosis factor related apoptosis inducing ligand (TRAIL), TRAIL receptor (TRAILR) 1, and TRAILR2 and down-regulation of Bcl2 and survivin."
